SELECT "s0"."Id", "s0"."AlbumId", "s0"."Duration", "s0"."Genre", "s0"."ReleaseDate", "s0"."Title", "a"."Id", "a"."ArtistId", "a"."Genre", "a"."ReleaseYear", "a"."Title", "a0"."Id", "a0"."Genre", "a0"."Name"
FROM (
    SELECT "s"."Id", "s"."AlbumId", "s"."Duration", "s"."Genre", "s"."ReleaseDate", "s"."Title"
    FROM "Songs" AS "s"
    ORDER BY "s"."Title"
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS "s0"
INNER JOIN "Albums" AS "a" ON "s0"."AlbumId" = "a"."Id"

FROM (
    SELECT "s"."Id", "s"."AlbumId", "s"."Duration", "s"."Genre", "s"."ReleaseDate", "s"."Title"

SELECT "p1"."Id", "p1"."CreationDate", "p1"."Title", "p1"."UserId", "s0"."PlaylistId", "s0"."SongId", "s0"."Id", "s0"."AlbumId", "s0"."Duration", "s0"."Genre", "s0"."ReleaseDate", "s0"."Title", "s0"."Id0", "s0"."ArtistId", "s0"."Genre0", "s0"."ReleaseYear", "s0"."Title0", "s0"."Id1", "s0"."Genre1", "s0"."Name"

    FROM "Playlists" AS "p"
    WHERE "p"."Id" = @__id_0
    LIMIT 1
) AS "p1"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT "p0"."PlaylistId", "p0"."SongId", "s"."Id", "s"."AlbumId", "s"."Duration", "s"."Genre", "s"."ReleaseDate", "s"."Title", "a"."Id" AS "Id0", "a"."ArtistId", "a"."Genre" AS "Genre0", "a"."ReleaseYear", "a"."Title" AS "Title0", "a0"."Id" AS "Id1", "a0"."Genre" AS "Genre1", "a0"."Name"
    FROM "PlaylistSongs" AS "p0"
    INNER JOIN "Songs" AS "s" ON "p0"."SongId" = "s"."Id"
    INNER JOIN "Albums" AS "a" ON "s"."AlbumId" = "a"."Id"
    INNER JOIN "Artists" AS "a0" ON "a"."ArtistId" = "a0"."Id"
) AS "s0" ON "p1"."Id" = "s0"."PlaylistId"
ORDER BY "p1"."Id", "s0"."PlaylistId", "s0"."SongId", "s0"."Id", "s0"."Id0"

SELECT "p1"."Id", "p1"."CreationDate", "p1"."Title", "p1"."UserId", "s0"."PlaylistId", "s0"."SongId", "s0"."Id", "s0"."AlbumId", "s0"."Duration", "s0"."Genre", "s0"."ReleaseDate", "s0"."Title", "s0"."Id0", "s0"."ArtistId", "s0"."Genre0", "s0"."ReleaseYear", "s0"."Title0", "s0"."Id1", "s0"."Genre1", "s0"."Name"
FROM (
    SELECT "p"."Id", "p"."CreationDate", "p"."Title", "p"."UserId"
    FROM "Playlists" AS "p"
    WHERE "p"."Id" = @__id_0
    LIMIT 1
) AS "p1"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT "p0"."PlaylistId", "p0"."SongId", "s"."Id", "s"."AlbumId", "s"."Duration", "s"."Genre", "s"."ReleaseDate", "s"."Title", "a"."Id" AS "Id0", "a"."ArtistId", "a"."Genre" AS "Genre0", "a"."ReleaseYear", "a"."Title" AS "Title0", "a0"."Id" AS "Id1", "a0"."Genre" AS "Genre1", "a0"."Name"
    FROM "PlaylistSongs" AS "p0"
    INNER JOIN "Songs" AS "s" ON "p0"."SongId" = "s"."Id"
    INNER JOIN "Albums" AS "a" ON "s"."AlbumId" = "a"."Id"
    INNER JOIN "Artists" AS "a0" ON "a"."ArtistId" = "a0"."Id"
) AS "s0" ON "p1"."Id" = "s0"."PlaylistId"
ORDER BY "p1"."Id", "s0"."PlaylistId", "s0"."SongId", "s0"."Id", "s0"."Id0"

2025-05-09 10:34:17.772 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (0ms) [Parameters=[@__p_1='?' (DbType = Int32), @__p_0='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT "s0"."Id", "s0"."AlbumId", "s0"."Duration", "s0"."Genre", "s0"."ReleaseDate", "s0"."Title", "a"."Id", "a"."ArtistId", "a"."Genre", "a"."ReleaseYear", "a"."Title", "a0"."Id", "a0"."Genre", "a0"."Name"
FROM (
    SELECT "s"."Id", "s"."AlbumId", "s"."Duration", "s"."Genre", "s"."ReleaseDate", "s"."Title"
    FROM "Songs" AS "s"
    ORDER BY "s"."Title"
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS "s0"
INNER JOIN "Albums" AS "a" ON "s0"."AlbumId" = "a"."Id"
INNER JOIN "Artists" AS "a0" ON "a"."ArtistId" = "a0"."Id"
ORDER BY "s0"."Title"

    LIMIT 1
) AS "p1"

    SELECT "p0"."PlaylistId", "p0"."SongId", "s"."Id", "s"."AlbumId", "s"."Duration", "s"."Genre", "s"."ReleaseDate", "s"."Title", "a"."Id" AS "Id0", "a"."ArtistId", "a"."Genre" AS "Genre0", "a"."ReleaseYear", "a"."Title" AS "Title0", "a0"."Id" AS "Id1", "a0"."Genre" AS "Genre1", "a0"."Name"

2025-05-09 12:24:31.443 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (0ms) [Parameters=[@__p_1='?' (DbType = Int32), @__p_0='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT "s0"."Id", "s0"."AlbumId", "s0"."Duration", "s0"."Genre", "s0"."ReleaseDate", "s0"."Title", "a"."Id", "a"."ArtistId", "a"."Genre", "a"."ReleaseYear", "a"."Title", "a0"."Id", "a0"."Genre", "a0"."Name"
FROM (
    SELECT "s"."Id", "s"."AlbumId", "s"."Duration", "s"."Genre", "s"."ReleaseDate", "s"."Title"
    FROM "Songs" AS "s"
    ORDER BY "s"."Title"
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS "s0"
INNER JOIN "Albums" AS "a" ON "s0"."AlbumId" = "a"."Id"
INNER JOIN "Artists" AS "a0" ON "a"."ArtistId" = "a0"."Id"
ORDER BY "s0"."Title"

2025-05-09 12:25:00.185 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (0ms) [Parameters=[@__id_0='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT "p1"."Id", "p1"."CreationDate", "p1"."Title", "p1"."UserId", "s0"."PlaylistId", "s0"."SongId", "s0"."Id", "s0"."AlbumId", "s0"."Duration", "s0"."Genre", "s0"."ReleaseDate", "s0"."Title", "s0"."Id0", "s0"."ArtistId", "s0"."Genre0", "s0"."ReleaseYear", "s0"."Title0", "s0"."Id1", "s0"."Genre1", "s0"."Name"
FROM (
    SELECT "p"."Id", "p"."CreationDate", "p"."Title", "p"."UserId"
    FROM "Playlists" AS "p"
    WHERE "p"."Id" = @__id_0
    LIMIT 1
) AS "p1"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT "p0"."PlaylistId", "p0"."SongId", "s"."Id", "s"."AlbumId", "s"."Duration", "s"."Genre", "s"."ReleaseDate", "s"."Title", "a"."Id" AS "Id0", "a"."ArtistId", "a"."Genre" AS "Genre0", "a"."ReleaseYear", "a"."Title" AS "Title0", "a0"."Id" AS "Id1", "a0"."Genre" AS "Genre1", "a0"."Name"
    FROM "PlaylistSongs" AS "p0"
    INNER JOIN "Songs" AS "s" ON "p0"."SongId" = "s"."Id"
    INNER JOIN "Albums" AS "a" ON "s"."AlbumId" = "a"."Id"
    INNER JOIN "Artists" AS "a0" ON "a"."ArtistId" = "a0"."Id"
) AS "s0" ON "p1"."Id" = "s0"."PlaylistId"
ORDER BY "p1"."Id", "s0"."PlaylistId", "s0"."SongId", "s0"."Id", "s0"."Id0"
